---
title: Creamy Chicken & Vegetable Pie with Cheesy Crushed Potato Topping
description: If we had to choose an entry for the 'Pie Most Likely To Please' competition, we'd be nominating this one. It has tender chunks of chicken thigh and veggies cocooned in a creamy sauce flavoured with thyme and mustard, topped off with chunks of tender crushed potato and a cheesy Cheddar crust. It's a winning combination you can't help but love.
